{"word":"ὑπεροπλίζομαι","slug":"ὑπεροπλίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπεροπλίζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ίσομαι</el>) (3rd sg. epic aor1 <a href='S:optative mood'>opt.</a> <el>-οπλίσσαιτο</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὁπλίζω'><el>ὁπλίζω</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to vanquish by force of arms</i>, or (from <a href='S:ὑπέροπλος'><el>ὑπέροπλος</el></a>) <i>to treat scornfully</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}